BT 0 g /F2 16 Tf 85.44 600 Td (Chapter 3: Setting Up Your Channel) Tj ET
q 0 G 1 w 60 585 m 372 585 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 560 Td (Create a Google account dedicated to your YouTube channel if you prefer separation.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 538 Td (Go to youtube.com and click Create a Channel to start your setup process.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 516 Td (Choose a channel name that is memorable, searchable, and reflects your content.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 494 Td (Write a channel description explaining what you make and who it helps.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 472 Td (Include keywords in your description that people might search for.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 450 Td (Create a channel banner \(2560 x 1440 pixels\) using Canva free templates.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 428 Td (Upload a professional-looking profile picture, ideally a clear photo of your face.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 406 Td (Add links to your social media and website in the channel About section.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 384 Td (Create a channel trailer: a 60-second video telling new visitors what to expect.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 362 Td (Set up channel sections to organize your videos by topic or series.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 340 Td (Verify your account by phone to unlock features like custom thumbnails.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 318 Td (Complete every section of your channel setup before publishing your first video.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 213.6 30 Td (3) Tj ET

endstream
