BT 0 g /F2 16 Tf 70.08000000000001 600 Td (Chapter 6: Editing Basics \(Free Tools\)) Tj ET
q 0 G 1 w 60 585 m 372 585 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 560 Td (DaVinci Resolve is professional editing software that is completely free.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 538 Td (iMovie comes free on Mac and is perfect for beginners with simple projects.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 516 Td (CapCut is free on mobile and desktop with excellent auto-caption features.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 494 Td (Import your footage, trim the beginning and end, and remove obvious mistakes.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 472 Td (Cut out long pauses, ums, ahs, and tangents that do not add value.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 450 Td (Add simple text on screen to emphasize key points during your video.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 428 Td (Include background music at low volume to fill silence and add energy.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 406 Td (Use royalty-free music from YouTube Audio Library which is free for creators.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 384 Td (Add jump cuts to remove dead space and keep the pacing energetic.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 362 Td (Export at 1080p resolution for the best balance of quality and file size.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 340 Td (Editing a ten-minute video takes one to three hours when you are starting out.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 318 Td (Speed improves dramatically with practice. Your tenth edit will be twice as fast.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 213.6 30 Td (6) Tj ET

endstream
endobj
