BT 0 g /F2 16 Tf 96.96000000000001 600 Td (Chapter 9: YouTube SEO and Tags) Tj ET
q 0 G 1 w 60 585 m 372 585 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 560 Td (YouTube SEO helps your videos appear when people search for your topic.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 538 Td (Research keywords using YouTube search suggestions: type your topic and note suggestions.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 516 Td (Include your main keyword in the title, description, and spoken in the video.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 494 Td (YouTube automatically transcribes videos so mentioning keywords verbally helps ranking.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 472 Td (Write descriptions of at least 200 words including relevant keywords naturally.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 450 Td (Add timestamps in your description which helps both viewers and search algorithms.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 428 Td (Use 5-10 relevant tags including your main keyword and related variations.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 406 Td (Tags are less important than title and description but still contribute to discovery.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 384 Td (Hashtags in your description \(3-5 maximum\) help categorize your content.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 362 Td (Your first 48 hours of performance heavily influence long-term ranking.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 340 Td (Encourage comments and engagement which signal to YouTube that your content has value.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 318 Td (Watch time is the most important ranking factor: make content people watch completely.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 213.6 30 Td (9) Tj ET

endstream
endobj
