BT 0 g /F2 16 Tf 62.400000000000006 600 Td (Chapter 12: Engaging with Your Community) Tj ET
q 0 G 1 w 60 585 m 372 585 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 560 Td (Reply to every comment on your videos, especially in the early growth phase.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 538 Td (Responding to comments signals to YouTube that your video has active engagement.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 516 Td (Heart comments from viewers to acknowledge them even when you cannot reply to all.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 494 Td (Ask questions in your videos to encourage viewers to leave comments.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 472 Td (Create community posts \(polls, updates, questions\) to stay visible between uploads.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 450 Td (Use the community tab to ask what content your audience wants next.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 428 Td (Pin a comment on each video with a question or additional resource link.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 406 Td (Acknowledge recurring commenters by name to build personal connections.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 384 Td (Create a Discord server or Facebook group for your most engaged viewers.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 362 Td (Go live occasionally to interact with your audience in real time.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 340 Td (Loyal community members become your biggest promoters who share your content.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 318 Td (Building genuine relationships with viewers matters more than any algorithm hack.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 211.2 30 Td (12) Tj ET

endstream
endobj
