BT 0 g /F2 16 Tf 73.92000000000002 600 Td (Chapter 13: Monetization Requirements) Tj ET
q 0 G 1 w 60 585 m 372 585 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 560 Td (YouTube Partner Program requires 1000 subscribers and 4000 watch hours in 12 months.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 538 Td (Alternatively, you need 1000 subscribers and 10 million Shorts views in 90 days.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 516 Td (Once accepted, you earn revenue from ads that play before and during your videos.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 494 Td (Average CPM \(payment per 1000 ad views\) ranges from 2 to 15 dollars depending on niche.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 472 Td (Finance, business, and technology niches earn the highest ad revenue per view.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 450 Td (You do not need monetization to earn money. Affiliate links work from day one.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 428 Td (Promote relevant products in descriptions and earn commission on sales.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 406 Td (Sponsors will approach you even before 1000 subscribers if your niche is valuable.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 384 Td (Sell your own digital products, courses, or services to your audience.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 362 Td (Super Chats during live streams let viewers pay to highlight their messages.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 340 Td (Channel memberships offer monthly subscription perks to your loyal viewers.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 318 Td (Diversify income streams so you never depend solely on YouTube ad revenue.) Tj ET
