q 0 G 1 w 60 585 m 372 585 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 560 Td (Days 1-7: Set up your channel completely. Film and publish your first two videos.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 538 Td (Days 8-14: Publish video three and four. Share on social media and ask for feedback.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 516 Td (Days 15-21: Analyze your first videos' analytics. Note what got the most watch time.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 494 Td (Days 22-30: Publish videos five through eight. Begin experimenting with Shorts.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 472 Td (Month 1 goal: 8 long-form videos published, channel fully optimized.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 450 Td (Days 31-45: Focus on titles and thumbnails. Study what makes viewers click.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 428 Td (Days 46-60: Engage in communities, comment on other channels, and collaborate.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 406 Td (Month 2 goal: 12 total videos, improving quality, beginning community engagement.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 384 Td (Days 61-75: Double down on content that performed best. Create related series.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 362 Td (Days 76-90: Analyze all data. Refine your content strategy based on what works.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 340 Td (Month 3 goal: 20+ videos published, clear content strategy, growing momentum.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 318 Td (After 90 days of consistent effort, you will have a foundation for long-term growth.) Tj ET
